(
<figureCitation box="[158,323,1004,1029]" captionStart="FIGURES 22 – 27" captionStartId="9.[151,264,1951,1974]" captionTargetBox="[220,1367,494,1920]" captionTargetId="figure@9.[186,1410,481,1940]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURES 22 – 27. Ruppeliana serrana sp. nov. 22, male holotype (total length 10.0 mm), dorsal view (antennae and legs not depicted), MNRJ. Male genitalia: 23, pygofer, valve, and subgenital plate, lateral view; 24, valve and subgenital plate, ventral view; 25, connective and style, dorsal view; 26, aedeagus, lateral view; 27, aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1005228/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="444">Figures 22–27</figureCitation>
